Original Release date:    September 27, 2000

Wizards & Warriors is a role-playing video game for Microsoft Windows. You control a party of player characters through a first person perspective, with turn based fights.

The player builds a team of up to six members from ten available races to fulfill the legend of the Mavin Blade. It is possible to choose between four professions to start with, and convert to eleven others during the game, as the player learns the destiny of the heroes and prepares to confront the evil Cet.
